description: Total number of interior nodes in all essentially series series-parallel networks with n labeled edges, multiple edges allowed.
references: J. W. Moon, Some enumerative results on series-parallel networks, Annals Discrete Math., 33 (1987), 199-226 (the e.g.f. I_S(x)).
links: Index entries for sequences mentioned in Moon (1987)
formula: E.g.f. = (xP'-P)/(1+U), where P = e.g.f. for A000311 and U that for A006351.
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Dec 20 2000
